OL,3,CWelsh Government 'not delivered' on
OL,4,Cdevolution of policing, says Plaid MS
OL,6,FA senior Senedd member has criticised
OL,7,Fthe Welsh Government for 'not
OL,8,Fdelivering' on the devolution of
OL,9,Fpolicing in Wales, amid proposals for
OL,10,Fwidespread reforms.
OL,12,FSioned Williams told ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,13,FSharp End: "We were promised
OL,14,Fdevolution of police and criminal
OL,15,Fjustice by this Welsh Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment and nothing has been
OL,17,Fdelivered on it."
