OL,3,CWelsh Government 'not delivered' on
OL,4,Cdevolution of policing, says Plaid MS
OL,6,FIt comes as the Westminster Government
OL,7,Fannounced plans to drastically reform
OL,8,Fpolice forces in Wales and England.
OL,9,FAlthough the proposals did not include
OL,10,Fplans to hand the Welsh Government
OL,11,Fpowers to decide how policing is run.
OL,13,FWatch in full on Youtube
OL,15,FMs Williams said: "We can have a
OL,16,Fconsultation, but we've had commission
OL,17,Fafter commission, independent experts
OL,18,Ftell us that the communities of Wales
OL,19,Fwould be best served by a devolved
OL,20,Fpolicing, and that also criminal
OL,21,Fjustice has to come with that as well."
