OL,6,FSam Rowlands, Conservative MS for
OL,7,FNorth Wales, said, "I think there are
OL,8,Ffar more important things right now to
OL,9,Fbe getting our teeth stuck into that
OL,10,Fneed sorting out in Wales and whether
OL,11,Fsomething like police should be
OL,12,Fdevolved or not.
