OL,3,CWelsh Government 'not delivered' on
OL,4,Cdevolution of policing, says Plaid MS
OL,6,F"We've seen far too many people on our
OL,7,Fwaiting lists, and our education
OL,8,Fstandards not being where it should
OL,9,Fbe... I'd like to see a government
OL,10,Fwhich puts all it's energy into
OL,11,Fsorting things out it's currently
OL,12,Fresponsible for, rather than being
OL,13,Fdistracted by these constitutional
OL,14,Fdebates all the time."
OL,16,FLeader of Torfean Council, and Labour
OL,17,Fcandidate, Anthony Hunt defended his
OL,18,Fparty: "What matters really is the
OL,19,Fimpact on communities, on policing,
OL,20,Fand how we make our communities safer,
OL,21,Fhow we all work together.
