OL,3,CWelsh Government 'not delivered' on
OL,4,Cdevolution of policing, says Plaid MS
OL,6,F"I think the way this white paper
OL,7,Fstarted with that consultation is so
OL,8,Fthat all levels of government will be
OL,9,Finvolved in that is exactly the right
OL,10,Fway to take it. Yes, I believe in the
OL,11,Fdevolution of policing as a part of
OL,12,Fthat journey, but I think what matters
OL,13,Fmost is that we start talking about
OL,14,Fwhat will make a difference in our
OL,15,Fcommunities."
